

Edge node
---------

You need to start ad egde node on each PC you want to connect with the *same*
community.

0. become root

1. create tun device
# tunctl -t tun0

3. enable the edge process
# ./edge d tun0 -c mynetwork -k encryptme -a 1.2.3.4 -l a.b.c.d:xyw


Supernode
--------

You need to start the supernode once

1. ./supernode -l 1234 -v


